    certificate rotation on a remote, the dialog re-probes the configured
    nodes, lets you accept the new fingerprint per node or clear the stored
    pin, and applies every accepted change as one batch. Reachable from the
    remotes list and offered directly on a PVE or PBS remote whose connection
